Package com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude

Class SolicitudeData

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.SolicitudeData
All Implemented Interfaces:
DownloadRegistry, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
SolicitudeData.Delayed, SolicitudeData.Verified
public class SolicitudeData extends Object implements Serializable, DownloadRegistry
Contains the information collected from a request at different stages. It can be used to restore a Solicitude to a given state.
Since:
1.0
Version:
